msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_FLUFF_0"
msgstr ""
"The lands of Law embrace you and forgive your little excursion. Welcome back "
"citizen."

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_FLUFF_1"
msgstr ""
"As you set foot back onto the lands of Law, you feel the refreshing vigor of "
"the land welcome you."

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_FLUFF_2"
msgstr ""
"The land around you seems comfortable and law abiding once more, you made it "
"back just in time!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_FLUFF_3"
msgstr ""
"You return to the Lawful Lands. The temptations of the Lawless did not take "
"you it seems!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_FLUFF_4"
msgstr ""
"The lawless lands did not claim your loyalty, you return safely to the lands "
"of Law."

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_FLUFF_5"
msgstr ""
"You return relatively unscathed to the Lands of Law, and your soul seems "
"none the worse off for spending some time among the rogues and villains of "
"the Lawless areas."

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_FLUFF_6"
msgstr ""
"You return safely to the Lands of Law, the Powers that Be welcome you with "
"no admonishment or judgement for your brief foray."

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_OWNED_BY_PLAYERS_UNWELCOME_FLUFF_0"
msgstr ""
"Greetings. This city has deemed you unwelcome! Leave, within the next %1 "
"seconds, lest all who see you consider you a rogue!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_OWNED_BY_PLAYERS_UNWELCOME_FLUFF_1"
msgstr ""
"While your lawful nature may find you welcome in most places, this is not "
"one of them! Here you are rogue! (unless you leave the city limits within %1 "
"seconds)."

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_OWNED_BY_PLAYERS_UNWELCOME_FLUFF_2"
msgstr ""
"Your kind ain't welcome in these here parts. Begone lest your smoldering "
"remains are swept out with a broom! Should you choose to remain, you will be "
"considered rogue within %1 seconds."

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_OWNED_BY_PLAYERS_UNWELCOME_FLUFF_3"
msgstr ""
"Lawful you may be, but welcome you be not! Leave the city limits within %1 "
"seconds or be officially branded a rogue!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_OWNED_BY_PLAYERS_WELCOME_FLUFF_0"
msgstr ""
"Welcome citizen. This city applauds your lawful ways and hopes you will "
"enjoy all that it has to offer!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_OWNED_BY_PLAYERS_WELCOME_FLUFF_1"
msgstr ""
"Good day Lawful one. This city deems you worthy and welcome within it's "
"walls!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_OWNED_BY_PLAYERS_WELCOME_FLUFF_2"
msgstr ""
"Welcome to the city! All citizens of good nature are deemed worthy to enjoy "
"the benefits offered within these humble walls."

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_OWNED_BY_PLAYERS_WELCOME_FLUFF_3"
msgstr ""
"Greetings friend! Within these city walls your lawful nature is always "
"weclome! Keep the peace!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWLESS_AREA_FLUFF_0"
msgstr ""
"A Law abiding citizen has no business in these lands! You have %1 seconds to "
"turn back!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWLESS_AREA_FLUFF_1"
msgstr ""
"You have now entered the Lawless Lands! You have %1 seconds before the "
"Powers that be reject you and you become a friend of Chaos!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWLESS_AREA_FLUFF_2"
msgstr ""
"You are now in lands governed by the minions of the lawless. In %1 seconds "
"you shall be considered the same as these rogues!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWLESS_AREA_FLUFF_3"
msgstr ""
"Welcome to the Lawless Lands. In %1 seconds your actions will be your own. "
"You shall be a rogue!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWLESS_AREA_FLUFF_4"
msgstr ""
"No guts, no glory! After %1 seconds you'll be free to earn glory, or end up "
"gutless!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWLESS_AREA_FLUFF_5"
msgstr ""
"You have stepped into the lands of chaos. In %1 seconds you shall be "
"considered a rogue. Neither your actions, or those taken against you shall "
"be judged!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWLESS_AREA_FLUFF_6"
msgstr ""
"There is no justice in these lands except that bestowed by the sword! In %1 "
"seconds you will join the ranks of the lawless!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWLESS_AREA_FLUFF_7"
msgstr ""
"You have left the lands of Law. The rule of Law shall forsake you in %1 "
"seconds!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_BLUE_ENTERING_LAWLESS_VILLAGE_AREA_FLUFF_0"
msgstr ""
"A Law abiding citizen has no business in these lands! You have %1 seconds to "
"turn back!"

