msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_IN_LAWLESS_AREA_AFTER_PRAYING"
msgstr "^Cred^WARNING!^N^ You are in a^Cred^ lawless^N^ area!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_IN_LAWLESS_AREA_AFTER_PRAYING_FLUFF_0"
msgstr ""
"Your prayer (and gold) has been accepted as appropriate tithe. Your standing "
"as a citizen of good has been returned. However you must leave these lands, "
"because in %1 seconds you will be branded a rogue!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_IN_LAWLESS_AREA_AFTER_PRAYING_FLUFF_1"
msgstr ""
"Gold and prayer have returned you to the lawful path. However the lands "
"around you are Lawless, and you will become rogue in %1 seconds! Leave now "
"or risk your newly returned status!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_IN_LAWLESS_AREA_AFTER_PRAYING_FLUFF_2"
msgstr ""
"You have earned your Lawful status once more! However these lands are no "
"longer welcoming to you! Make haste and depart them, because in %1 seconds "
"you will be returned to the status of rogue!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_IN_LAWLESS_AREA_AFTER_PRAYING_FLUFF_3"
msgstr ""
"Your pious prayers (and glittering gold) have brought you back to the ways "
"of Law. The lands around you, however, are lawless! Get you back to the safe "
"havens quickly, because in %1 seconds you will be rogue!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_IN_LAWLESS_VILLAGE"
msgstr "^Cred^WARNING!^N^ You are in an^Cred^ active^N^ village area!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_FLUFF_0"
msgstr "An aura of Law assaults your senses. In these lands YOU are the prey!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_FLUFF_1"
msgstr "You have entered the lands of Law, be wary lawless one."

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_FLUFF_2"
msgstr ""
"Enter these lands at your own risk. In the lands of Law, the friends of "
"chaos are the hunted."

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_FLUFF_3"
msgstr ""
"You're now in the lands of Law. Harming the lawful will have consequences "
"here."

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_FLUFF_4"
msgstr ""
"Murder is against the law, and as these are its lands, keep your weapon in "
"its sheath!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_FLUFF_5"
msgstr "Lawful Lands. Stay Alert, you are basically free loot here."

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_OWNED_BY_PLAYERS_UNWELCOME_FLUFF_0"
msgstr ""
"This city deems your lawless ways unwelcome! Leave lest you incur the wrath "
"of the clan!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_OWNED_BY_PLAYERS_UNWELCOME_FLUFF_1"
msgstr "Your lawless status is unwelcome within these city walls. Begone!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_OWNED_BY_PLAYERS_UNWELCOME_FLUFF_2"
msgstr ""
"Your kind ain't welcome in these here parts. Begone lawless one lest your "
"smoldering remains are swept out with a broom!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_OWNED_BY_PLAYERS_UNWELCOME_FLUFF_3"
msgstr ""
"Your lawless ways have made you unwelcome in this city. It is best that you "
"leave before there is little left of you."

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_OWNED_BY_PLAYERS_WELCOME_FLUFF_0"
msgstr ""
"Welcome Lawless One! Within these city walls the clan considers you a friend!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_OWNED_BY_PLAYERS_WELCOME_FLUFF_1"
msgstr ""
"Within the limits of this city, your lawless ways bear no judgment or "
"admonishment. Be welcome!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_OWNED_BY_PLAYERS_WELCOME_FLUFF_2"
msgstr ""
"None shall judge your lawless ways within these city-walls. Welcome and have "
"a nice day!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_AREA_OWNED_BY_PLAYERS_WELCOME_FLUFF_3"
msgstr ""
"The city has weighed and judged you and found your lawless ways...without "
"fault! Welcome friend!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_VILLAGE_AREA_FLUFF_0"
msgstr "An aura of Law assaults your senses. In these lands YOU are the prey!"

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_VILLAGE_AREA_FLUFF_1"
msgstr "You have entered the lands of Law, be wary lawless one."

msgid "NOTIFICATION_AREA_ALIGNMENT_RED_ENTERING_LAWFUL_VILLAGE_AREA_FLUFF_2"
msgstr ""
"Enter these lands at your own risk. In the lands of Law, the friends of "
"chaos are the hunted."

